disasters.description: Tropical Cyclone Cyber has developed in the Tasman Sea and is currently located to the west-northwest Cheviot Beach, Victoria in Demo Land. The storm has been moving away from the island nation with winds of 110 kilometres per hour and gusts as high as 140km/h. Warnings have been issued for the possibility of flooding rains and damaging winds.
